metadata.name: The Choco Taco NFT
metadata.description: Choco Taco is 'the original ice cream taco' Klondike discontinued the Choco Taco in July 2022, but we said NOPE. And bought thousands of them, one Choco Taco for each NFT in fact. They will be stored, forever, in these big Costco Freezers and the Choco Taco will NEVER DIE. Actually, it is up to you. Each Choco Taco NFT represents a real Choco Taco in our Choco Taco Treasury. IF you so choose to burn your Choco Taco NFT, your IRL Choco Taco will be sent to you. With Great power comes great responsibility. Choco Taco Forever, Mozzy out.
